pacoteco: pacoteco (Tool to create Slackware package templates)
pacoteco:
pacoteco: This tool generates a template for creating Slackware packages.
pacoteco: It includes a script and a tarball with a sample package structure.
pacoteco: Run 'pacoteco <name> <version>' to create a new template.
pacoteco: Run 'pacoteco <version> -s' to create a new SlackBuild script.
pacoteco:
pacoteco: Author: Ruben Carlo Benante <rcb@beco.cc>
pacoteco: Homepage: https://beco.cc/downloads/slackware/pkgs/
pacoteco: License: GNU GPL V3
pacoteco:
